{"tid":2433212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國有民調指七成人認為應促進中國人權　即使經濟受損","createTime":"2021-03-04T21:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T00:05:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d83cf8a542a9d9d767d36ba223e9084426140e9","tid":2433212,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T21:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578828-20210305.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578828-20210305.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUtOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=c84806fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578828-20210305.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a884bb4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578828-20210305.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國再有民調指當地民眾對中國態度轉差。<br />\n<br />\n總部設在華盛頓的智庫皮尤研究中心，上月訪問了2500名美國民眾，七成人認為即使傷害兩國經濟關係，華府亦應該促進中國人權發展；89%成年人將中國視為競爭對手或敵人，而不是夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指出，分別有65%及50%受訪者，認為來自中國的網絡攻擊，及中國的人權政策，對美國來說是非常嚴重的問題，兩個比率都較去年上升7個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n另外，分別有53%及52%受訪者，認為美國就業機會流失到中國，以及中國軍事實力增強，對美國來說是非常嚴重的問題，兩個比率都較去年上升6個百分點。三成一受訪者就認為，內地與香港的關係，對美國來說是非常嚴重的問題，比率較去年上升5個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n美國民調機構蓋洛普早前公布的調查指出，美國民眾對中國的好感程度降至新低。在北京，外交部日前回應，指美國上屆政府及美國國內反華勢力，出於意識形態偏見及一己政治私利，大肆抹黑中國，肆意挑動對抗和分裂，散布政治病毒，嚴重毒化兩國民意氣氛；中方希望美方客觀理性看待中國及中美關係，採取理性務實對華政策。"},{"pid":"736a5df9141d3a05066bed397fb5f78cdcb3a4de","tid":2433212,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:59:46.000Z","msg":"美國左膠：<br />\n請唔好歧視中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人權最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港新疆抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddd15b4e108bbe34c477e1b689cc0413dc86464","tid":2433212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cf8a4562a535adf6dd6016b6b9b49a99070275","tid":2433212,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:04:21.000Z","msg":"但個訪問得2500個受訪者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196bd4ed4423677c67077cdfa3f82c7b429da739","tid":2433212,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:05:53.000Z","msg":"China Joe：唔可以歧視中國，要同中國合作<br />\n <img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-EZ8T06iNl4/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F-EZ8T06iNl4%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=3323aaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/9oiieqfZ81M/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F9oiieqfZ81M%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=ea7e8534&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}